##For the first time in seven years, the supermarket has become a battlefield

Micro Signal thelivings

The function introduction, reconstructs our life with the narrative beauty.

She wants the epidemic to go away. Cough when the people around no longer dodge; in and out of the community no longer need to bring a few papers; every morning when the door, the first sight is still the egg "eye-coveting" of the elderly.

Image courtesy | SIPA

Cheng was a colleague of mine when I worked as a cashier at a supermarket in Jiangsu Province a few years ago. She was diligent, kind, and took good care of me. It's just that we haven't seen each other for years, and we don't talk much, and we only greet each other during the holidays.
On the first day of the New Year this year, as usual, I sent a New Year's greeting to sister Cheng, but in the past few days there was no reply. It was the beginning of the outbreak, and the news of the closure of Wuhan made it difficult to escape from my mind -- The supermarket was on lockdown all year round, even during the Spring Festival, and I was worried for her.
It wasn't until February 5th that she texted me back. I quickly asked her how things are, whether the New Year has been working in the supermarket. She was silent for a moment, then told me what happened in the supermarket this Spring Festival.

Before New Year's Eve, Cheng returned to her hometown of Chongqing.
In 2018 Spring Festival, sister Cheng's cousin married, sister Cheng's family did not go back, the mother is very sorry, so early this year informed a family, in any case, also want to rush back to Chongqing home for the New Year. To this end, Cheng Jie booked a month in advance of the 4 sleeper tickets, and to the supermarket asked for 10 days off, the original fifth day back to work.
This is the first time in several years that sister Cheng has asked for leave during the Spring Festival. In previous years at this time, she still kept checking out guests at the counter, "On the one hand, it's hard to get a holiday because of the shortage of staff at the supermarket at the end of the year. On the other hand, Statutory Holidays are paid three times as much. "
Cheng Jie's family is not rich, a family of 4 people have been working outside for many years, in addition to her family also has a younger brother, in the neighboring city factory work. Neither brother nor sister had a family, and the family lived together until the younger brother moved to a rented house near the factory. Cheng Jie had also entered the factory, did not work for a long time to resign, and later introduced to the supermarket to apply for, a dry is 7 years. Because of her work, she almost said goodbye to the holidays all these years.
Holidays are always the best time for supermarket business. "The checkout line is like a ball of thread at the beginning. No matter how fast you pull, you can't pull it clean. ".
Years ago, Chengjie in the supermarket experience the first small long holiday on her mind: From 8 am on the machine scanning the code, the head has not raised. I do not know how many gift boxes swept, shopping bags used one after another, the Cup of boiling water until it was too cold to drink.
Lunch shift shift, control (a function of the cashier class, mainly to the cashier dispatch) accidentally missed Cheng Jie, she did not care about the time. Until 3 o'clock in the afternoon, the deputy director came to give her change before she whispered she did not eat, the deputy director was surprised, quickly replaced her, also called her a "fool. ".
Clean machine in the evening, Cheng Jie is almost collapsed on the bench, sitting in the classroom for a long time before going home.
Think of this year can have a good Spring Festival, Cheng elder sister in a good mood, stand the last shift, set the working group as "news do not disturb. ".

The train departure time on the evening of January 21, this morning, the parents took his brother to the mall to buy new clothes and shoes, Cheng Jie a person at home tidying up, in the afternoon when they returned, Cheng Jie found that there are several brand new masks inside.
"Your cousin just called and said there was some serious infection recently. Let's remember to wear this on the way. " That said, the mother's tone was full of disapproval, she also stuffed several masks into her luggage.
In the afternoon, a family started off with a big bag and a small bag. On the way to the bus, it began to rain. The family was caught in the rain and the wind, making her feel very uncomfortable. She was very depressed. After she got on the bus and settled down with her luggage, she couldn't hold on any longer, soft climb to the top bunk, soon fell asleep. Wake up in the middle of the night to pour water, only to find that sleeping in their bottom bunk is a little girl, all the way did not talk, is very quiet. The girl was wearing a mask and was somewhat evasive towards sister Cheng. "In retrospect, it's understandable. After all, we didn't follow my cousin's advice to wear a mask at first, and she was so sick that of course she was afraid. "
At 9:00 a.m. on January 23rd, they finally made it home. After getting out of the car, Cheng Jie opened the mobile phone only to know that Wuhan was closed.
In her hometown for a few days, although the discussion about the epidemic was heated, Cheng Jie knew that they didn't take it seriously, and her parents had the same idea, "It's good to see what's on the Internet, and everyone believes that their life is not over yet? " One sentence choked Cheng to silence, "To be honest, I wasn't really on my guard at the time, and I certainly didn't take it as lightly as they did, and I didn't want to spread rumors or anything. I just wanted my parents to be a little more alert, at least to wear the mask. "
Little effect, family members and friends including parents or do not wear masks, cousin said they are "ignorant fearless" , Cheng sister thought deeply.
The next day to the home, sister Cheng's cold aggravated, cough more severe, to the town hospital to buy medicine, the doctor is very alert to her, temperature has been asked her from where, have not passed Wuhan, because of what illness? Ching managed a few words. The doctor wrote out only two prescriptions and said, "come back when you're done. The government says we're not closing for a while. ". Fortunately, the medicine was good, and Ching got better soon.
On the third day of the Lunar New Year, Cheng and her family returned home as planned, and the journey was very different from when they arrived: The railway station added checkpoints to measure her body temperature, and even when she slept on the train, she was woken up by the conductor to take her temperature. Cheng sister secretly glad he bought medicine in his hometown, otherwise even if there is no fever, so serious cold will probably be stopped down. When the community at the door to measure the body temperature and set up a card when the people came into view, Cheng Jie just know: This a few days ago seems far away from their own war, in the end can not stay out of it.

According to the original plan, the next day Cheng sister back to the supermarket to work. However, she just arrived home, received a notice from the head of the class: working hours to be determined, a few days at home isolation observation. The class leader is afraid that Cheng Jie wants more, then explains: "This is not against you a person, everyone is like this, after all is special period. "
There was no reason for the chief to be afraid of Cheng's overthinking: In addition to the base salary, nearly half of the cashier's salary came from working hours, and any time over 40 hours a week was overtime. So in order to facilitate the overall arrangement, cash register class set up nearly 10 different time periods of the frequency. Some are very long, from 8am to 8pm, for 12 hours, known as the "Devil Shift" by colleagues; some are very short, come at 9am and can go back at 12pm.
There is usually a day or two of rest each week, the day is not fixed. If it rains and there are few people, you can leave work early. The head of the class should try to keep everyone's shift level so as to avoid a large pay gap between the cashiers.
Now the director let Cheng sister to work a few days late, meaning that this month Cheng sister's salary will shrink again.
Safety First, Cheng Jie of course understand, "in fact, the director is to think too much, what she is, I am the most clear. "
Cheng Jie remembers when she first arrived at the supermarket, she was not used to the chaos of the shift. Especially the first week, even though she had taken a picture of the schedule on her cell phone, she would still forget or misread it, either too early or too late, several Times I got a call from the class president, and I was like, "why aren't you at work? " "Didn't I have a 9:00 shift today? " "Who told you? Look at this week's schedule. You were supposed to be here at 8:00! " And it wasn't until the next month that things got better.
The class president was then in his 30s, smart and capable, to that pestle will have a not angry and authoritative momentum. Sister Cheng was afraid of her at first, but it took her a long time to realize that she was a mean person.

Cheng Jie this just opened the work group that is shielded, spent half a day to glance through, just know in oneself leave of these days, what happened in the supermarket.
On January 25, the first day of the Lunar New Year, the supermarket held a lucky draw according to the original plan. All customers can participate with receipts after they have bought 200 yuan. This activity supermarket had been warming up for more than half a month years ago, the leader of the day also repeated in the group: "guests if the amount of shopping is not much, remember to remind, ask them whether they need to buy more items to make up the bill, so as not to cause customer complaints. "
However, the event lasted only half a day before it was called off. Surprisingly, the customers of the supermarket "back and forth" is not entangled, are very understanding. In the past, this would have been almost impossible
Chengjie also remembers the mid-autumn Festival in previous years, the supermarket did a discount: a brand of edible oil by membership card to enjoy a 70% discount, each membership card to buy a maximum of 2 barrels. One customer was so excited that he had to tow two shopping carts full, only to be told of the restrictions when he checked out at sister Cheng's. In fact, such a large bill of goods, generally will have a guide to help explain clearly, perhaps the day of shortage of staff, guide did not have time to explain.
Cheng Jie advised customers to push the car to the side, to other guests borrow a good membership card after the bill. The man didn't want to, "No one told me when I bought it upstairs, " she said. "I didn't have to go to all this trouble to find out. I don't care what you think. You have to give me a discount today. "
Cheng Jie can only inform the central control to deal with, the first time the central control contact the upstairs guide, but the guide did not come in time. The section chief sees the guest manner is tough, can let the guest of the back first go to other machine table to line up. There are so many people in the mid autumn festival that it takes more than 10 minutes to reach each station, and many customers feel as if they are already in the front of the queue.
In the midst of all this chatter, the customer who had bought the oil was coming in, and his voice was getting louder and louder. For the first time, sister Cheng stood by in silence, not knowing what to do. The director with walkie-talkies to urge the upstairs guide down to explain clearly, while the vice director from the hands of the control is not much, let her take a pen and paper to the other guests quickly borrow a membership card.
Unexpectedly, the oil buyer saw that he had the upper hand and became increasingly arrogant. He suddenly pulled down the name tag on Cheng's chest and shouted, "I will go to the counter (customer service) to complain about you if you don't handle it well! "
The sudden "sneak attack" scared sister Cheng, but the head of the class quickly dragged her behind him, and at the same time angrily shouted: "What are you doing! " The oil man refused to give in, his mouth began to burst out of profanity, some towards the supermarket, some of them are after the class president and sister Cheng.
Customers around the situation are quiet, some of the line soon quietly turned to the other machine checkout. Stuck in the middle, unable to move, can only pretend to play with the phone.
At daggers drawn, Cheng Jie was vice-president pulled back to the classroom. She did not see the situation behind, only to hear that the head of the class called security, finally did not make things worse. In the end, he scraped together a dozen membership cards to settle his bill.
This kind of thing is not uncommon in supermarkets. It happens almost every few days. Cheng Jie remembers last year's National Day when there are guests for a package of promotional tissue in the call center big fight, and finally even alarm the police.
Today, the event was canceled without comment, leaving her to marvel at the tolerance and restraint of her often high maintenance clients as she headed toward the outbreak.

Rest at home for a few days, February 2, the ninth day of the Lunar New Year, Cheng Jie finally received a notice from the class president: "tomorrow to come to work, many people have not rested for more than 20 days, it can not hold up. "
In fact, the supermarket has always been the practice of hiring winter workers, but in the past two years, the cash register area has added a number of self-service cash registers, relieving some of the pressure on staff, so the temporary decision to reduce the number of people, only a few years ago recruited less than five winter workers. Before she returned home, there were fewer than 30 students in the class, far fewer than in previous years.
But the cash register is not so easy to use, payment method is limited, the efficiency is not high, most customers do not want to learn to use, can be a cashier to share the pressure is limited. After the beginning of the year is even more difficult, the five college students all called to say that they could not come, the cash register class can not recruit new people, the pressure increased sharply. Add a few and Cheng Jie, like home visit, at this time the cash register class has less than 20 people struggling to support.
The section chief confirmed two questions to sister Cheng repeatedly; "Do you have a fever or other discomfort? Have you passed Wuhan? " Sister Cheng replied no, the section chief just sent sister Cheng's schedule for the next week.
On the Tenth Day of the Lunar New Year, Cheng went to work for the first time in two years.

The restaurant, not far from the staff aisle where the temperature was taken, was open, its tables covered with foam, its stalls divided, and its red-hatted guides eating.
There was no one to speak in the dining room, only the faint clatter of cutlery. Cheng Jie see their masks are not off, Taut to pin on the chin, Kan Kan exposed mouth. A person finished eating ready to get up, quickly pulled on the mask, to the side of the colleagues nodded to go to the sink washed chopsticks, the whole process without any communication.
Cheng sister some trance, the past so many years, every restaurant is noisy, we are at work time suppressed impulse to talk here to be released, eating seems to be just a thing.
After the second floor of the staff channel, Cheng Jie across the supermarket to his classroom. Every Spring Festival, in the main entrance on the second floor, the supermarket will set up a "New Year Street" , which is filled with all kinds of bulk candy fried goods, stretching for 10 meters until the other side of the supermarket, not until the Lantern Festival.
But this year, this "street" also lost, the original flow of people on the second floor is relatively less desolate. She did not know when it was withdrawn, but it seemed reasonable. "How can the street be so lively when the real street is empty out there? "
On Duty, control in addition to give Cheng Jie issued a mask, but also gave her a pair of rubber gloves and a pair of goggles. Cheng was surprised until she noticed that her colleagues at the cash register were all heavily armed, and goggles and face masks were standard issue.
As for the gloves, they're also for the cashier at the supermarket. After all, with money to deal with every day, wearing gloves can minimize direct contact. It's just that when these things are put on, Cheng's voice is much quieter when she talks to guests in polite language, which she doesn't think most people can hear. "That used to be a big no-no! "
To make a good impression on customers, the head office has designed a set of polite phrases for cashiers that require everyone to be correct in every word when receiving customers.
In fact, customers rarely care, but the supermarket is very important to this. Headquarters sends special people down to make unannounced visits every month. These people will disguise themselves as customers to buy goods. If they find any irregularities in the employees, they will report them. After each store receives the list at the end of the month, they will report the criticisms and at the same time, they will also be fined, serious even to go to the human resources department "learning transformation. ".
Because of polite language, Cheng Jie in the beginning of the occupation was also the class president "focus on defense" for a period of time.
This set of polite language is not long, from beginning to end only about 50 words, but very formal and written. Cheng Jie is not good at communicating with people, this paragraph can not be said in any case. Even if you do manage to say it out loud, it's as quiet as a mosquito humming, barely audible to anyone else. This of course is not pass, the chief of the class several times when the inspection machine will remind her attention. But as nature would have it, it's far from easy to overcome. But, the section chief will try his best to arrange a less conspicuous place for Cheng Jie when arranging the machine, let her take advantage of no one when their own practice.
The effect of this move is really limited, Cheng sister still said to stutter. The director herself did not feel at ease. When she was doing nothing, she came to pay attention to the progress of Cheng Jie. After all, she did not know when the "mystery guest" from headquarters would come and where she would go, but people in their own classrooms are always embarrassed when they're caught.
At that time, sister Cheng every day to work are scared, afraid that they will be on the "mystery guest" list. There is no danger is, Cheng Jie was not "caught" , polite language also said more and more good, soon do not need a long "focus on defense" .
However, under the current special circumstances, supermarkets have also relaxed their restrictions in this regard, "It's hard to hear the polite language now, it's slow to change with the gloves on, and I don't hear any more accusations or complaints. In that sense, I kind of like it. "
Of course, it's still poignant after the joke.

Back to work after Cheng Jie know, in their own back to work the night before, the supermarket fresh class Yan Fang asked for help, said the community closed, oneself can not go home.
Yan Fang lives in a neighborhood not far from the supermarket and is only 10 minutes away by electric bike. After the Chinese New Year, the area was closed, and access was strictly controlled, with no one allowed in or out before 6 a.m. or after 10 p.m. , except for a pass. Yan FANGFA message is blocked in the community door, she took a photo of the community door to the group: the other two female residents of the same night off work sitting in the car, looking at the guard booth. Two guards stand in the guard box, watching helplessly, watching them in silence. The size of the community two iron gates were tightly closed, leaving no gap. It was 10:05 p.m. , just five minutes past the prescribed closing time.
Yan Fang said he had called the police, but the police came to no avail, a group of people confrontation in the cold night, he had no choice but to ask the leadership for help.
In the group soon someone replied "received" , but since then no following, follow-up Yan Zhengfang how to return home, Cheng elder sister do not know.
On the second day, while the supermarket leaders informed the classrooms to collect the identity cards of the people who worked in the morning and those who worked late, and hoped that they could be notified by the government departments to let them pass, they also reported the matter to the local industrial and commercial departments, the response came quickly: "All units in the district can use the "pass" and "unit certificate" free access to the community. The former in their own residential area; the latter is issued by the Unit Human Resources Department
At first the two proofs did have some effect; at least no one in the group reflected on them. But the certificate only applies to the city community, until 8:30 on the evening of February 8, clothing class Deng Minzhi report, he was stopped in the road.
Deng, who lives in a nearby city, commutes to work by bike for more than an hour each day. That evening she went home from work with two colleagues who also lived in the city next door, but was stopped at a checkpoint on the border between the two cities and refused to let her through. A few days before that, it was just a matter of showing your ID and checking in.
Everyone had their passes and passes on them, but the people at the checkpoint didn't recognize them. Deng Minzhi begged: "I really live in the city, tomorrow I do not come out? " The reply is still no.
Deng was so worried by the roadside that he almost burst into tears. "They didn't let me through until 6 o'clock. I can't stand here all night. "
The crowd gave them advice, some people let her take the path, Deng Minzhi hurriedly asked where the path, the move of the people did not move, but another person jumped out and said: "No use, the path has long been sealed. "
Still have a person to let Deng Minzhi turn round come back, oneself home can lend her to stay overnight. Many more echoed the sentiment, with some even saying that staying in their homes for a long time would not be a problem. Deng Minzhi declined: "Do not know how long this matter will make, the total can not always live in your there? "
After much discussion, a few of Deng could only ask the supermarket leader for help.

The message of help soon alarmed the store manager. The store manager contacted the head of the three people, let them understand the situation first, placate the three employees; while on the phone, he found the store manager of the local Bureau of Industry and Commerce and the stores in the neighboring city, and asked them to coordinate with the relevant units in the neighboring city to see if they could release the person. The result of the coordination is not ideal, the people at the checkpoints do not feed into oil and salt, only the local registered residents into the city, otherwise no one is useful. But Deng Minzhi 3 people in the neighboring city only temporarily lives, the Hukou is in the other place, all does not meet the condition.
Toss for more than half an hour without result, the store manager also had no idea, can only let the section chiefs arrange, send 3 people to the colleague home of this city first, tomorrow from long-term plan again. The section chief contacted several colleagues who had cars at home and asked them to drive to the checkpoint to pick them up. That this matter has been settled by a narrow margin.

On Feb. 4, someone posted online that employees at other branches of the supermarket had lied about their husbands'return from Wuhan, telling people to stop shopping at the supermarket. The rumor ferments very quickly, many people follow under the post "thanks reminds" . More rumors followed, including rumors that many local supermarkets and vegetable farms would close down after the 10th.
It was impossible for the supermarket to ignore this kind of news, and during that time, the supermarket leaders were busy trying to dispel the rumors. In addition to posting statements on their official websites, they also contacted local government media accounts around the country to help clarify the matter. At the same time, the supermarket in Wuhan Branch as early as the beginning of the epidemic began to carry out a number of material assistance, the leadership of the relevant photos to the group, let everyone in the circle of friends more publicity.
People are angry at such rumors, and there is a sense of shared hatred. Cheng Jie also felt very bad, for her, they just do their job, of course, not great. But from the overall point of view, the supermarket is another sense of the front line, Cheng Jie really do not want to see someone without reason to slander.
"In fact, a lot of people in the supermarket are afraid and standing in this position with a stiff upper lip. I don't understand what kind of mentality these scaremongers have. "
Fortunately, the supermarket has been in normal operation, there is no shortage of materials, rumors self-defeating. The only change is that starting from February 10, the supermarket has changed its opening hours from 8:00-22:00 to 9:00-20:00, so as long as things are done in the evening, no customers will be able to get off work early, unless, of course, this is mainly for home appliances, clothing, selling non-essential goods of the classroom, fresh, vegetables and fruits such areas are still full during the day, leaving work early simply can not be talked about.
These days, although the supermarket is not short of supplies, in order to minimize the number of trips, most customers come to buy food and daily necessities for several days at a time, when the checkout time every shopping cart is filled to the brim, the line goes from morning to evening every day.
Cheng Jie every day heavily armed, scanning code swept the world dark, every time the central control notice off work, for her is a great relief. By the time I got back to class and took off my mask and goggles, the sweat on my face had soaked the mask. Even so, it is absolutely can not take it lightly, the class president will be in the group repeatedly daily reminder, "to wear a suction valve mask to keep away from the guests. ".
The store quickly outfitted its staff with raincoats and face masks, which were modified from summer sun hats, on top of the original three-piece suit. But still some people are not quite at ease, such as entry about six months of Xiao Gao, in the raincoat before, in the supermarket hair mask inside a 3-layer disposable medical mask, wear goggles after the whole head like a round dumplings.
"Be afraid also is normal. " Cheng Jie remembered a few days ago when oneself cleaned lightly coughed twice, the person next to drew away body like an electric shock, after the reaction is embarrassed, but the look in the eyes is still showing caution and caution. At that moment, she was nostalgic for the mornings before the outbreak -- Every morning in the supermarket
At 8:00 a.m. , The staff pulled up the shutters to open for the day. Every time the door opened, the old man and woman who had been waiting outside rushed in, galloping, flocking to the egg selling area. It's no secret that there are a limited number of eggs on sale at the supermarket in the early morning. As a result, grandfathers and grandmothers will "crouch" outside the door before the supermarket is open so that they can stand in line several more times to grab more eggs, this is what happens in the supermarket every morning.
In the past, every time on the morning shift to see such a scene, Cheng Jie will unconsciously smile. Sometimes she even thought of her own old age, and how happy it would be if she could keep up her spirits in old age. After all, for most people, worrying about food and water is the most life-like thing. It's just that she hasn't seen anything like it since she went back to work this year.
These days, to say that the hot is still related to the epidemic of disinfection, protective supplies. Supermarkets have been selling washable cotton masks, which have been snapped up even though they have little protection against the virus. Many people in order to seek a psychological comfort, will be in the medical mask cover a layer of cotton mask.
In addition to face masks, sales of hand sanitizer and hand sanitizer are up significantly, with most shoppers bringing along a few bottles. On Feb. 16, supermarkets began limiting purchases of hand sanitizer to three bottles per membership card. Cash Register class also made a special announcement in the group: No internal staff to buy the bill, "in fact, this is completely unnecessary, we do not even have time to shop. "

Postscript

Since the start of the work, sister Cheng has had a rest for half a day. The pressure of the cash register class is still very heavy. After the business hours were adjusted, there have also been several occasions when the customers have not finished leaving after the 8 p.m. closing time. The cash register class can only keep two or three channels open, check them out before you leave.
Two days ago a family member died in a residential area, in the past, we will put 3 days of banquet, accompanied by music to send away the deceased. Now, with the outbreak, we have to keep things simple.
That day Cheng Jie off work, saw them in the community under the tree lit a fire, a few people wearing filial piety is in the fire of low-pitched sob. Mournful music is recorded in advance with the mobile phone, when playing the volume is turned up to the maximum, sharp suona sound wave after wave in the hearts of people, in the cold night even more heartbreaking.
In this situation, Cheng elder sister more miss every morning when the door, the first sight is the egg "eye-covetous" of the Old Lady's Day.

At that time, sister Cheng every day to work are scared, afraid that they will be on the "mystery guest" list. There is no danger is, Cheng Jie was not "caught" , polite language also said more and more good, soon do not need a long "focus on defense" .

However, under the current special circumstances, supermarkets have also relaxed their restrictions in this regard, "It's hard to hear the polite language now, it's slow to change with the gloves on, and I don't hear any more accusations or complaints. In that sense, I kind of like it. "

Of course, it's still poignant after the joke.

Back to work after Cheng Jie know, in their own back to work the night before, the supermarket fresh class Yan Fang asked for help, said the community closed, oneself can not go home.
Yan Fang lives in a neighborhood not far from the supermarket and is only 10 minutes away by electric bike. After the Chinese New Year, the area was closed, and access was strictly controlled, with no one allowed in or out before 6 a.m. or after 10 p.m. , except for a pass. Yan FANGFA message is blocked in the community door, she took a photo of the community door to the group: the other two female residents of the same night off work sitting in the car, looking at the guard booth. Two guards stand in the guard box, watching helplessly, watching them in silence. The size of the community two iron gates were tightly closed, leaving no gap. It was 10:05 p.m. , just five minutes past the prescribed closing time.
Yan Fang said he had called the police, but the police came to no avail, a group of people confrontation in the cold night, he had no choice but to ask the leadership for help.
In the group soon someone replied "received" , but since then no following, follow-up Yan Zhengfang how to return home, Cheng elder sister do not know.
On the second day, while the supermarket leaders informed the classrooms to collect the identity cards of the people who worked in the morning and those who worked late, and hoped that they could be notified by the government departments to let them pass, they also reported the matter to the local industrial and commercial departments, the response came quickly: "All units in the district can use the "pass" and "unit certificate" free access to the community. The former in their own residential area; the latter is issued by the Unit Human Resources Department
At first the two proofs did have some effect; at least no one in the group reflected on them. But the certificate only applies to the city community, until 8:30 on the evening of February 8, clothing class Deng Minzhi report, he was stopped in the road.
Deng, who lives in a nearby city, commutes to work by bike for more than an hour each day. That evening she went home from work with two colleagues who also lived in the city next door, but was stopped at a checkpoint on the border between the two cities and refused to let her through. A few days before that, it was just a matter of showing your ID and checking in.
Everyone had their passes and passes on them, but the people at the checkpoint didn't recognize them. Deng Minzhi begged: "I really live in the city, tomorrow I do not come out? " The reply is still no.
Deng was so worried by the roadside that he almost burst into tears. "They didn't let me through until 6 o'clock. I can't stand here all night. "
The crowd gave them advice, some people let her take the path, Deng Minzhi hurriedly asked where the path, the move of the people did not move, but another person jumped out and said: "No use, the path has long been sealed. "
Still have a person to let Deng Minzhi turn round come back, oneself home can lend her to stay overnight. Many more echoed the sentiment, with some even saying that staying in their homes for a long time would not be a problem. Deng Minzhi declined: "Do not know how long this matter will make, the total can not always live in your there? "
After much discussion, a few of Deng could only ask the supermarket leader for help.

On Feb. 4, someone posted online that employees at other branches of the supermarket had lied about their husbands'return from Wuhan, telling people to stop shopping at the supermarket. The rumor ferments very quickly, many people follow under the post "thanks reminds" . More rumors followed, including rumors that many local supermarkets and vegetable farms would close down after the 10th.
It was impossible for the supermarket to ignore this kind of news, and during that time, the supermarket leaders were busy trying to dispel the rumors. In addition to posting statements on their official websites, they also contacted local government media accounts around the country to help clarify the matter. At the same time, the supermarket in Wuhan Branch as early as the beginning of the epidemic began to carry out a number of material assistance, the leadership of the relevant photos to the group, let everyone in the circle of friends more publicity.
People are angry at such rumors, and there is a sense of shared hatred. Cheng Jie also felt very bad, for her, they just do their job, of course, not great. But from the overall point of view, the supermarket is another sense of the front line, Cheng Jie really do not want to see someone without reason to slander.
"In fact, a lot of people in the supermarket are afraid and standing in this position with a stiff upper lip. I don't understand what kind of mentality these scaremongers have. "
Fortunately, the supermarket has been in normal operation, there is no shortage of materials, rumors self-defeating. The only change is that starting from February 10, the supermarket has changed its opening hours from 8:00-22:00 to 9:00-20:00, so as long as things are done in the evening, no customers will be able to get off work early, unless, of course, this is mainly for home appliances, clothing, selling non-essential goods of the classroom, fresh, vegetables and fruits such areas are still full during the day, leaving work early simply can not be talked about.
These days, although the supermarket is not short of supplies, in order to minimize the number of trips, most customers come to buy food and daily necessities for several days at a time, when the checkout time every shopping cart is filled to the brim, the line goes from morning to evening every day.
Cheng Jie every day heavily armed, scanning code swept the world dark, every time the central control notice off work, for her is a great relief. By the time I got back to class and took off my mask and goggles, the sweat on my face had soaked the mask. Even so, it is absolutely can not take it lightly, the class president will be in the group repeatedly daily reminder, "to wear a suction valve mask to keep away from the guests. ".
The store quickly outfitted its staff with raincoats and face masks, which were modified from summer sun hats, on top of the original three-piece suit. But still some people are not quite at ease, such as entry about six months of Xiao Gao, in the raincoat before, in the supermarket hair mask inside a 3-layer disposable medical mask, wear goggles after the whole head like a round dumplings.
"Be afraid also is normal. " Cheng Jie remembered a few days ago when oneself cleaned lightly coughed twice, the person next to drew away body like an electric shock, after the reaction is embarrassed, but the look in the eyes is still showing caution and caution. At that moment, she was nostalgic for the mornings before the outbreak -- Every morning in the supermarket
At 8:00 a.m. , The staff pulled up the shutters to open for the day. Every time the door opened, the old man and woman who had been waiting outside rushed in, galloping, flocking to the egg selling area. It's no secret that there are a limited number of eggs on sale at the supermarket in the early morning. As a result, grandfathers and grandmothers will "crouch" outside the door before the supermarket is open so that they can stand in line several more times to grab more eggs, this is what happens in the supermarket every morning.
In the past, every time on the morning shift to see such a scene, Cheng Jie will unconsciously smile. Sometimes she even thought of her own old age, and how happy it would be if she could keep up her spirits in old age. After all, for most people, worrying about food and water is the most life-like thing. It's just that she hasn't seen anything like it since she went back to work this year.
These days, to say that the hot is still related to the epidemic of disinfection, protective supplies. Supermarkets have been selling washable cotton masks, which have been snapped up even though they have little protection against the virus. Many people in order to seek a psychological comfort, will be in the medical mask cover a layer of cotton mask.
In addition to face masks, sales of hand sanitizer and hand sanitizer are up significantly, with most shoppers bringing along a few bottles. On Feb. 16, supermarkets began limiting purchases of hand sanitizer to three bottles per membership card. Cash Register class also made a special announcement in the group: No internal staff to buy the bill, "in fact, this is completely unnecessary, we do not even have time to shop. "

Postscript

Since the start of the work, sister Cheng has had a rest for half a day. The pressure of the cash register class is still very heavy. After the business hours were adjusted, there have also been several occasions when the customers have not finished leaving after the 8 p.m. closing time. The cash register class can only keep two or three channels open, check them out before you leave.
Two days ago a family member died in a residential area, in the past, we will put 3 days of banquet, accompanied by music to send away the deceased. Now, with the outbreak, we have to keep things simple.
That day Cheng Jie off work, saw them in the community under the tree lit a fire, a few people wearing filial piety is in the fire of low-pitched sob. Mournful music is recorded in advance with the mobile phone, when playing the volume is turned up to the maximum, sharp suona sound wave after wave in the hearts of people, in the cold night even more heartbreaking.
In this situation, Cheng elder sister more miss every morning when the door, the first sight is the egg "eye-covetous" of the Old Lady's Day.
